<abstract><t>This document presents an alternate method to do the anti-replay checks and updates for IP Authentication Header (AH) and Encapsulating Security Protocol (ESP).  The method defined in this document obviates the need for bit-shifting and it reduces the number of times anti-replay window is adjusted.</t></abstract>

